{"tid":1183631,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"身為利迷 我對球隊攞歐聯毫無感覺","createTime":"2019-06-03T05:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T16:02:13.000Z","uid":167940,"like":144,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6f7dd872c297aefb61b33b2a53e02e1fe37777","tid":1183631,"uid":167940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"好多人話我地失落左歐聯14年<br />\n由學神黑暗時代<br />\n到今日重回歐洲之顛<br />\n好應該值得高興<br />\n<br />\n但老實講<br />\n就算有幾多個歐聯獎杯<br />\n都唔比唔上攞一次我地從未攞過嘅本土冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n..<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jh9GULP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJh9GULP.png&h=ab13d6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一隊球隊<br />\n如果連草地都保養唔好<br />\n仲有咩值得高興？<br />\n<br />\n利迷一齊一叫<br />\nFSG out! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Klopp out! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曼聯調理農務草地專家in! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7042df1adbb05386820aa1e6d393a37a5240e400","tid":1183631,"uid":167940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"一齊大叫*"},{"pid":"9a05ccd71f2d8ba7cd4705eec8138beb59269665","tid":1183631,"uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"從未攞過嘅本土冠軍?"},{"pid":"af63a0cfbcf050372963c8e05a3a043dfdfc5078","tid":1183631,"uid":167940,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9a05ccd71f2d8ba7cd4705eec8138beb59269665","tid":1183631,"uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"從未攞過嘅本土冠軍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"草地泥土冠軍"},{"pid":"f059080d12eea3f0f341ac60337d1e6d2a69cf93","tid":1183631,"uid":23848,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"你up乜9"},{"pid":"32